{"tid":1907292,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府後日(3月4日)將派出2班包機到武漢接載港人 即日下午及黃昏後抵港","createTime":"2020-03-02T13:33:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-02T14:05:57.000Z","uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8d7e1a02646135b9b3f86b407ab0c35830acd2bd","tid":1907292,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:33:33.000Z","msg":"港府本周三(4日)將派包機到湖北武漢，接載港人返港，入境處處長曾國衞及政制及內地事務局局長聶德權會到武漢統籌，當日將會派出2班包機，已有港人收到當局電話查詢健康情況。據悉，現時仍有3000多名港人分布在該省37個大小城市。<br />\n<br />\n目前身處湖北的港人，今日(2日)下午陸續收到街道辦人員電話，表示可安排包機離開，「收到通知，如你們沒有發熱或其他症狀？可能於本周三或周四安排你們離開」。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會指，屆時會安排當區居委會義工車隊接載港人去機場。本周三會有兩班包機由香港飛到武漢，接載首批450名港人返港，由國泰港龍營運，每班機均有醫護人員隨行，預計下午及黃昏後抵達本港。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200302/bkn-20200302183322574-0302_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20200302%2Fbkn-20200302183322574-0302_00822_001.html&d=FoM%2FNT%2BxDvRLDdkWKwCN%2BLJtyMJyNHaGyUrVEdcKl1A%3D&h=7e5d1ffe\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20200302/bkn-20200302183322574-0302_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3bab4ee5a08019dd7ec3489108444d44f16a8bda","tid":1907292,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:35:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f54c94dd5b77ba7fdd50a7c4bc7cfcc4831a9d","tid":1907292,"uid":35456,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:38:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bda23298b39d72a9ff0fb0b1b302bac12236a806","tid":1907292,"uid":346806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-02T13:41:58.000Z","msg":"我生日先派包機 <br />\n食蛋糕都食得唔安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59aea7b476693f6230a04c330d1ab4517bc9db8a","tid":1907292,"uid":35456,"like